00:35:42,239 --> 00:35:44,958
He was in pole.
He was going be world champion,

492
00:35:45,079 --> 00:35:48,516
if he won the race.
The pressure was huge.

493
00:35:53,679 --> 00:35:56,193
We are about to start.
Green light.

494
00:35:56,480 --> 00:35:57,514
Senna does not start!

495
00:35:57,880 --> 00:35:59,677
Senna remains on the grid!

496
00:36:01,079 --> 00:36:04,992
Prost came out ahead
while Ayrton Senna was left behind.

497
00:36:06,920 --> 00:36:09,992
Ayrton Senna is in 14th place.

498
00:36:11,559 --> 00:36:12,788
I thought, "So long title. It's over".

499
00:36:12,880 --> 00:36:13,949
REGINALDO LEME
GLOBO TV COMMENTATOR

500
00:36:14,039 --> 00:36:15,188
"It's over."

501
00:36:19,119 --> 00:36:23,112
He takes eighth place.
An amazing comeback from Senna.

502
00:36:32,719 --> 00:36:35,153
Then his favourite thing happened,

503
00:36:35,239 --> 00:36:36,592
it began to rain.

504
00:36:38,440 --> 00:36:40,590
Senna is now in fourth position.

505
00:36:41,519 --> 00:36:44,353
Senna goes, goes, goes!

506
00:36:46,079 --> 00:36:49,038
Senna is getting close.
Senna is going to challenge for the lead.

507
00:36:49,360 --> 00:36:52,715
Ayrton Senna overtakes Prost and onwards!

508
00:36:52,800 --> 00:36:55,155
Ayrton Senna has got the lead.

509
00:37:02,280 --> 00:37:05,317
I started giving thanks
during the last lap.

510
00:37:05,480 --> 00:37:07,152
I thanked God

511
00:37:07,280 --> 00:37:11,193
It was incredible. I could not believe
I was going to win the championship,

512
00:37:12,360 --> 00:37:15,715
Despite all the anxiety and tension.

513
00:37:16,599 --> 00:37:18,476
I felt God's presence.

514
00:37:19,719 --> 00:37:21,789
I have seen God

515
00:37:22,599 --> 00:37:26,070
It was a very special moment for me.

516
00:37:26,920 --> 00:37:29,309
An indescribable feeling.

517
00:37:29,599 --> 00:37:34,309
It remains engraved in my
memory and as a part of me.

518
00:37:41,440 --> 00:37:44,556
Ayrton Senna of Brazil!

519
00:37:44,880 --> 00:37:49,431
World Champion 1988!

520
00:37:51,400 --> 00:37:53,867
SAO PAULO

521
00:38:04,280 --> 00:38:06,474
What an incredible race!

522
00:38:06,920 --> 00:38:13,108
A great victory.
He had to come from 16th place.

523
00:38:15,519 --> 00:38:20,878
AYRTON SENNA
WORLD CHAMPION 1988

524
00:38:25,679 --> 00:38:29,355
Ayrton, how do you feel
as World Champion?

525
00:38:29,639 --> 00:38:31,949
I feel so much peace.

526
00:38:32,320 --> 00:38:34,833
It is as if someone had removed
a huge weight

527
00:38:35,199 --> 00:38:37,349
from my shoulders and head.

528
00:38:37,519 --> 00:38:42,594
It is difficult to understand what it means
be a world champion.

529
00:38:43,440 --> 00:38:48,559
What do you say about a man who says
he has seen God in any circumstances

530
00:38:48,679 --> 00:38:50,670
never mind on the last lap of a Grand Prix,

531
00:38:50,760 --> 00:38:54,833
a few yards away from winning the World Championship.

532
00:38:56,199 --> 00:38:58,394
Most people would be skeptical.

533
00:38:59,599 --> 00:39:02,273
And I think most people would be right.

534
00:39:02,960 --> 00:39:05,393
Senna did seem to be absolutely convinced

535
00:39:05,480 --> 00:39:09,393
That he'd seen God.
He didn't say what God was,

536
00:39:09,559 --> 00:39:13,108
how God appeared to him in that moment,

537
00:39:16,239 --> 00:39:18,708
but it's his right to say that.

538
00:39:18,800 --> 00:39:22,509
He must have known that he would risk

539
00:39:23,679 --> 00:39:26,989
looking...well not looking a fool
but attracting skepticism.

540
00:39:30,599 --> 00:39:32,670
And who are we to

541
00:39:33,440 --> 00:39:38,753
challenge that really..
When anybody makes such a claim?

542
00:39:39,480 --> 00:39:44,235
But certainly this is unique
in the history of Grand Prix.

543
00:39:44,880 --> 00:39:47,188
When we are talking about God,

544
00:39:47,320 --> 00:39:49,275
First of all I believe in God too,

545
00:39:49,360 --> 00:39:53,751
but would never use
the same words Ayrton did.

546
00:39:54,119 --> 00:39:56,394
If you are in the same team,
doing the same business

547
00:39:56,480 --> 00:40:02,396
and taking risks with the other drivers
and team members,

548
00:40:03,159 --> 00:40:06,947
this kind of thing
does not make you very comfortable.

549
00:40:07,880 --> 00:40:13,193
because it is not only believing in God,

550
00:40:13,360 --> 00:40:20,117
but using that as a strength

551
00:40:20,639 --> 00:40:25,588
having always, the right.

552
00:40:25,679 --> 00:40:28,989
That is, he was thinking he was always right

553
00:40:29,079 --> 00:40:34,677
and in this case, it could be dangerous, on the track

554
00:40:35,079 --> 00:40:39,277
and i sometimes felt, not very comfortable.

555
00:40:40,320 --> 00:40:43,197
Yes, there were many cynics

556
00:40:44,400 --> 00:40:46,516
in Formula One

557
00:40:49,559 --> 00:40:51,835
who challenged whether this was

558
00:40:53,599 --> 00:40:57,990
and authentic and real

559
00:41:01,360 --> 00:41:05,034
account of what he felt
and what his values were.

560
00:41:06,199 --> 00:41:10,239
But y'know, I was there to witness it
very often

561
00:41:12,360 --> 00:41:19,072
in private environments,
and he was most defintely sincere.

562
00:41:19,960 --> 00:41:22,110
This is how he felt.

563
00:41:22,199 --> 00:41:25,748
He felt he was supported by

564
00:41:30,360 --> 00:41:33,875
the God that he believed in

565
00:41:33,960 --> 00:41:37,315
and why on earth would I

566
00:41:37,440 --> 00:41:41,353
or should anybody,
dissuade him from that belief?

567
00:41:41,440 --> 00:41:43,317
Because he

568
00:41:46,920 --> 00:41:50,434
was special, he was committed,

569
00:41:50,679 --> 00:41:54,992
and his strong belief, for me, is a good thing,
as long as they are positive ones.

570
00:41:55,599 --> 00:41:59,434
SAO PAULO
15th NOVEMBER 1988

571
00:42:12,880 --> 00:42:14,791
He is an amazing person, wonderful.

572
00:42:14,880 --> 00:42:19,550
He is very humble and improves the
image of Brazil abroad.

573
00:42:19,880 --> 00:42:22,030
He shares his victory with us.

574
00:42:22,199 --> 00:42:23,315
I admire him very much.

575
00:42:23,480 --> 00:42:24,548
He is very brave man.

576
00:42:24,639 --> 00:42:25,675
I just know this.

577
00:42:25,760 --> 00:42:26,875
We are proud of him.

578
00:42:27,639 --> 00:42:30,472
It is one of the few things
that we can still be proud of.

579
00:42:30,760 --> 00:42:34,309
Once, I asked Ayrton
"When will you think about quitting?"

580
00:42:34,400 --> 00:42:37,597
He said, "Mum, the day I am
the champion I will stop."

581
00:42:37,800 --> 00:42:41,030
In my heart,
I knew that was not true.

582
00:42:41,239 --> 00:42:42,389
We all know that.

583
00:42:43,199 --> 00:42:47,273
SENNA FAMILY HOME VIDEO

584
00:42:49,639 --> 00:42:52,074
SENNA'S FAMILY AND THE
FAMILY OF TAMIN ANGRA

585
00:42:53,320 --> 00:42:54,355
VIVIANE SENNA
AYRTON'S SISTER

586
00:42:54,440 --> 00:42:57,431
After the 1988 Championship,
after he won the title,

587
00:42:58,920 --> 00:43:04,233
We noticed that he had changed between
the beginning and the end of the year.

588
00:43:05,599 --> 00:43:09,797
Because he had found himself.

589
00:43:09,880 --> 00:43:12,074
He had discovered who he was.

590
00:43:12,159 --> 00:43:17,153
It was a process that reached
its conclusion after his championship victory.

591
00:43:26,440 --> 00:43:28,032
At Christmas, many things happen.

592
00:43:28,119 --> 00:43:29,472
New friends are made,

593
00:43:30,159 --> 00:43:32,036
like the person I'm about to introduce.

594
00:43:32,119 --> 00:43:33,155
XUXA MENEGHEL
BRAZILIAN TV STAR

595
00:43:33,800 --> 00:43:35,518
He was part of my 1988.

596
00:43:35,599 --> 00:43:37,476
Ayrton Senna.

597
00:43:46,119 --> 00:43:48,190
Isn't he cute?

598
00:43:49,480 --> 00:43:52,391
I have a few question for you.

599
00:43:53,320 --> 00:43:57,597
I think everybody is excited,
but none more than me,

600
00:43:57,679 --> 00:44:02,992
It is not easy to talk.
Ayrton is now my friend.

601
00:44:03,079 --> 00:44:06,197
Ayrton, what do you want for Christmas?

602
00:44:06,280 --> 00:44:08,429
As a Christmas present?

