00:44:14,480 --> 00:44:19,315
It should be censored.
Let's say I just want to be happy.

606
00:44:19,400 --> 00:44:21,391
Whisper it to me.

607
00:44:28,199 --> 00:44:29,871
Happy New Year.

608
00:44:30,679 --> 00:44:32,079
Happy 1990.

609
00:44:32,800 --> 00:44:34,677
Happy '91.

610
00:44:34,760 --> 00:44:36,273
Happy '92.

611
00:44:36,559 --> 00:44:38,630
Happy '93.

