00:51:21,079 --> 00:51:26,677
But Ayrton was convinced

709
00:51:27,000 --> 00:51:32,597
that it was a conspiration
and the story starts like this.

710
00:51:32,920 --> 00:51:34,797
and I am very sorry about that.

711
00:51:35,400 --> 00:51:39,871
I would like to give a warm welcome to
the President of FISA, Mr. Balestre.

712
00:51:42,960 --> 00:51:44,188
Please, gentlemen.

