It was rooted in the belief
that you didn't make contact,

1093
01:19:07,119 --> 01:19:08,519
with another rival's car,

1094
01:19:08,600 --> 01:19:10,158
because if you did that you're likely to die.

1095
01:19:10,760 --> 01:19:13,399
Two of the greatest champions
in the history of Formula One

1096
01:19:13,479 --> 01:19:14,993
