Championship ruined.

1097
01:19:15,079 --> 01:19:18,277
They accuse each other,
but Prost was the hardest.

1098
01:19:18,359 --> 01:19:19,917
His reaction was violent.

1099
01:19:20,000 --> 01:19:26,555
I wanted to punch him in the
face, but I was so disgusted

1100
01:19:26,640 --> 01:19:28,756
that I did not succeed.

1101
01:19:28,840 --> 01:19:30,353
It makes me feel sick.

1102
01:19:31,079 --> 01:19:35,231
Senna versus Prost which went on for a couple of seasons more

1103
01:19:35,359 --> 01:19:37,350
was just absolutely wonderful
for Formula One.

1104
01:19:40,560 --> 01:19:43,631
The television ratings improved.
Everything went up.

1105
01:19:43,720 --> 01:19:45,073
People talked about it.

1106
01:19:45,199 --> 01:19:48,350
It was controversial,
shocking and fascinating.

1107
01:19:50,920 --> 01:19:53,717
