02:20:28,479 --> 02:20:31,438
Seeing the helicopter going to the hospital,

1845
02:20:32,520 --> 02:20:35,317
I was still hoping.

1846
02:20:36,440 --> 02:20:37,918
I did not realize.

1847
02:20:39,120 --> 02:20:44,273
During the live commentary
I did not realize.

