02:23:50,520 --> 02:23:52,157
It was what he wanted to do.

1887
02:23:57,159 --> 02:24:00,994
And if that was the outcome...

1888
02:24:07,680 --> 02:24:10,911
linked to his career,

1889
02:24:12,280 --> 02:24:15,431
I do not think he would change it,
