1906
02:25:22,159 --> 02:25:26,073
That was just after the race, they did not know exactly what...

1907
02:25:26,520 --> 02:25:27,998
They were really shocked,

1908
02:25:28,079 --> 02:25:33,200
but again, they did not want to make any speculation and waiting for that.

1909
02:25:33,280 --> 02:25:37,318
We only knew from the track to the airport, more and more that it was

1910
02:25:37,399 --> 02:25:40,790
quite serious.

