02:25:41,280 --> 02:25:45,956
You reflect on the difficult things in your life and the extreme emotions

1912
02:25:48,440 --> 02:25:53,274
and inevitably things don't get better and
in that regard,

1913
02:25:53,360 --> 02:25:56,192
with the process of thought,

