02:26:35,680 --> 02:26:38,477
Ayrton Senna will always be fast.

1921
02:26:39,239 --> 02:26:40,958
He will never be old.

1922
02:26:41,719 --> 02:26:43,596
He will always be

1923
02:26:46,000 --> 02:26:47,352
the champion.

1924
02:26:48,520 --> 02:26:50,953
of Brazil and of the world.

1925
02:26:56,879 --> 02:27:00,270
The grief, even today,

1926
02:27:00,360 --> 02:27:05,388
